      "content": "make do with the emptiness... how do you even do that? it just feels like i'm waiting for something that’s never coming back. it’s like i’m just a ghost in my own life. i look at the future and it just looks like a huge, dark nothing. i don't think i want to spend the rest of my life just \"making do\" with being miserable.",
